** Events related

IEvent
    FetchTickEvent -> raised by atsys, used by DataFetcher to fetch ..
        List<Instrument>

	TickDataEvent -> raised by data fetcher, consumed by strategy

	SignalEvent-> raised by strategy , consumed by Portfolio manager
	OrderEvent -> raised by portfolio mgr , consumed by Execution handler
	FillEvent -> raised by execution handler , consumed by Perfomance metric recording service...



*** Core components ****


IDataFetcher
    // fetch data for a particular tick, may be cached or on the fly..
    // publish TickDataEvent


IStrategy
    initialize();
    onTick(TickDataEvent e);

    // create signal..
    // uses market tick and IPortfolio...


IPortfolioManager
    onSignal() // create Order


IExecutionHandler
    onOrder()  // create Fill


IPerformanceManager



